# Release News — Website Checklist

When new builds or a release happens, update the website in `web/marketing/blog.html`.

## Steps

1. **blog.html**: add `.news-card` at top of product-news in ALL 7 language blocks (`data-lang="uk|en|fr|es|de|it|el"`)
2. **Tag**: `"В розробці"` (amber `#F59E0B`) for unreleased, `"Реліз"` (purple `#7C3AED`) for released
3. **Commit & push**: `git add web/marketing/blog.html && git commit -m "blog: vX.X.X news" && git push`
4. **SCP to VPS**: `scp web/marketing/blog.html deploy@135.125.254.131:/var/www/im-in.net/html/`
5. **Verify**: `https://www.im-in.net/blog.html`

## Also update (in social-automation repo)

- `content/product_knowledge.py` — add feature Q&A sections
- `content/prompts.py` — update v1.0.x teaser in SYSTEM_PROMPT_FEATURE, ACTIVE_TRAVEL, LEISURE_TRAVEL

See `social-automation` rules: `prompts-knowledge.mdc`, `release-news-workflow.mdc`
